We have many skillful characters at our disposal who may be assigned to special missions in order to sway campaign conditions to our favor.  Each character has a unique set of abilities which make him or her more or less capable of succeeding at certain missions.  To examine a character's abilities, right-click on that character and select 'Status' from the pop-up menu.  In the Status Window you will see, among other items, a listing of the character's values in Diplomacy, Espionage, Combat, and Leadership. Many missions require skills in these areas; the higher a character's values are in a particular category, the more likely it is that they will succeed on a mission requiring that skill.  Other missions, such as Ship Design Research, require more specialized abilities; you can discover whether your character is capable of such missions by again examining their status window under `R&D capabilities'.